# Cloudflare redirects for Narramorph.
#
# The canonical-host redirect (www.narramorph.com -> narramorph.com, 301) is
# configured as a zone-level Redirect Rule in the Cloudflare dashboard
# (Rules -> Redirect Rules), not here: it runs at the edge before asset serving,
# is host-agnostic, and avoids platform-specific _redirects cross-host / force-flag
# quirks. See docs/RELEASE_ROLLBACK.md section 1.
#
# The app is hash-routed (#/passage/:id), so all real navigation is under "/", which
# serves index.html; genuinely unknown paths fall through to the branded 404.html.
# No same-host redirect is needed, so this file is intentionally comment-only.
